==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: commercialize
<hw>commercialize</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>to make something commercial
in character, either by placing it for sale on the open market, or by
emphasizing its profit-making aspects; <as>as, the Olympics have been
excessively <ex>commercialized</ex></as>.</def> <altsp>[Also spelled
<asp>commercialise</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>commercialized</ent>⟦br⟧
